lvdbg:
=====

A simple debugger front end.

BUILDING:
========

To build lvdbg run:

>autoreconf --install
>./configure
>make

See ./configure --help for configuration options.

To build developer documentation:

>make -C docs devel_docs

To run unit tests:

>make check

To see test coverage:

>make -C tests cov

The output coverage is in tests/lcov_html

Configuration:
=============
A example of a configuration file should be installed under the pkd_data
directory. The file is in data/ directory in the source tree.

